        <div id="reqWrap" style="padding: 7%">

            <div class="volunteerReqCard" id="commitmentBox" style="background-color: black; display: inline-block; width: 45%">

                <center>A three-quarter commitment, each involving:</center>

                <ul class="requirementList">
                    <li>2 mandatory clinic Saturdays</li>
                    <li>2 community service (outreach) events</li>
                    <li>1 fundraising event</li>
                    <li>Monday class attendance (class is held once a week from 6:00-7:00 PM) and committee participation</li>

                </ul>

                NOTE: 1 quarter leave may be taken upon fulfillment of the three-quarter commitment.

            </div>
            
            <div class="volunteerReqCard" id="healthClearanceBox" style="background-color: #831b05; float: right; width: 48%">

                <center>Health Clearance Requirements</center>

                <ul class="requirementList">

                    <li>Measles, Mumps, Rubella (MMR) : two lifetime doses (or blood test)</li>
                    <li>Varicella (Chickenpox Vaccine) : one lifetime dose (or blood test)</li>
                    <li>TB (Quantiferon or PPD Skin Test, Two Step) : COMPLETE YEARLY</li>
                    <li>Flu Shot (Fluvirin) : COMPLETE YEARLY</li>
                    <li> HIPAA Certification: Complete the <a class="embeddedLink" href="http://www.ucdmc.ucdavis.edu/compliance/Quiz/PrivacySecurity/player.html" target="_blank" style="color:red">training</a> and screenshot the certificate at the end. COMPLETE YEARLY</li>


                </ul>

